messages.ssml: <speak>According to the World Health Organization, there are many different coronaviruses (CoV). They can cause illnesses ranging from the common cold to more severe lung infection. <sub alias="covid 19">COVID-19</sub> is the disease caused by the new or "novel" coronavirus.</speak>

messages.speech: According to the World Health Organization, there are many different coronaviruses (CoV). They can cause illnesses ranging from the common cold to more severe lung infection. COVID-19 is the disease caused by the new or "novel" coronavirus.
